TITLE: TypeScript Definitions for Hrana v2 Request Types
DESCRIPTION: Type definitions that extend the Hrana v1 protocol with new request types: SequenceReq, DescribeReq, StoreSqlReq, and CloseSqlReq, along with their corresponding response types.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tursodatabase/libsql/blob/main/docs/HRANA_2_SPEC.md#2025-04-11_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
type Request =
    | ...
    | SequenceReq
    | DescribeReq
    | StoreSqlReq
    | CloseSqlReq

type Response =
    | ...
    | SequenceResp
    | DescribeResp
    | StoreSqlReq
    | CloseSqlReq
```

