TITLE: Creating Test Database with Tables and Views in SQLite
DESCRIPTION: SQL script that generates a test database containing multiple tables with INTEGER, TEXT, and NULL values. Creates various views demonstrating different SQL operations including JOINs, UNIONs, recursive queries, and aggregations. The script also includes indexes and constraints like PRIMARY KEY and UNIQUE.
